snippet.title: 10 Min Full Body HIIT Workout to Get Fit! All Standing, No Planks | MYLEE Home Fitness
snippet.description:
Hello everyone, this is Full Body HIIT Workout for about 13 minutes.
It is a home training program designed to help you not only lose weight without special equipment at home, but also get a slim and elastic body. 
There are 12 exercises performed in HIIT Workout (High-intensity interval training) and all movements are performed according to the beat, so you can concentrate more and have fun without getting bored.
In addition, since it's all standing movements and no planks, there is no need for equipment such as fitness mat and there is no need to lie on the floor.
Hope you have a good workout.

- Time : 13 Min
- Exercises : 12
- No Equipment

Caution!
